document_data.Description:
[[File:Spinner's Prison Rift opens.jpg|300px|thumb|''The Spinner tears open the Rift and meets her maker.'']]
{{Quote
|The Rift is growing bigger, day by day, minute by minute. Eventually it will consume all of our world.<br/>We Gatekeepers must remain here and use our magics to slow the Rift's growth as best we can. This is why we need a hero like you to venture inside the Rift and tell us what lies inside.
|[[Tavnar Kronnak]]
}}
The Rift served primarily as a means of egress for the [[Spinner of Shadows]] so that she could rejoin [[Lolth]] and abscond from Eberron with a large amount of [[dragonshard]]s. As a bonus, the ''portal'' would continue to grow on its own and eventually consume the entire world of Eberron, adding its ruins to Lolth's domain.
